snippet.title: New Galactic Strongholds Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official  Galactic Strongholds announcement trailer and get ready to customize your personal Strongholds and launch your Guild Flagship in the new Free-to-Play Digital Expansion, Galactic Strongholds, coming this summer!

Subscribe by May 11, 2014 to receive Early Access on June 24th plus a luxurious NAR SHADDAA SKY PALACE STRONGHOLD with THREE ADDITIONAL ROOMS UNLOCKED!

For more information, visit www.swtor.com/galactic-strongholds 

PLAY FREE NOW: www.swtor.com/play-free

Stay connected through our Community Blog, Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, Instagram and Twitch!
